{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-template-tsx","path":"/absinthe/custom-scalar-types","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>need to define:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>parse - converts value from user to elixir code</li>\n<li>serialize - converts value from elixir to JSON</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>scalars can be used as input or output types</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\"><pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">query</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  users<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">addedBefore</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2019-01-01\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    name\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"elixir\"><pre class=\"language-elixir\"><code class=\"language-elixir\"><span class=\"token comment\"># schema</span>\nscalar <span class=\"token atom symbol\">:date</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span>\n  parse <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> input <span class=\"token operator\">-></span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> Date<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>from_iso8601<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>input<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token atom symbol\">:ok</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> date<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token atom symbol\">:ok</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> date<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      _ <span class=\"token operator\">-></span> <span class=\"token atom symbol\">:error</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\n\n  serialize <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> date <span class=\"token operator\">-></span>\n    Date<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>to_iso8601<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>date<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"date":"April 11, 2021","path":"/absinthe/custom-scalar-types","title":"Custom Scalar Types","category":"Absinthe"}}},"pageContext":{}}}